General Mechanics:
- Naming: Allows you to name yourself and animal companions
- Health: You have a starting hitpoints that can be raised through story progression
- Stamina: Stamina is consumed when using dodge rolls or running in combat
- Save points: The game has safe locations to save your progress
- Achievements: Allows players to obtain rewards for their progress
- Experience: Leveling up allows the player to better their character
- Inventory: Players have a limited inventory to use
- Bartering: Some NPCs will have the ability to trade, buy, and sell

Combat Mechanics:
- Dodge: Allows player to dodge roll in the direction they are facing or walking
- Block: Player can block incoming physical damage
- Duel Weilding: Players can equip two weapons or spells but cannot use a shield to block when doing so
